** '''Duke Horacio:''' We were recently sorting through some of the things stored down in the cellar, and we found this old talisman.
** {{tbox|pic=Air talisman detail.png|The Duke shows you a talisman.}}
** '''Duke Horacio:''' The Order of Wizards over at the Wizards' Tower have been on the hunt for magical artefacts recently. I wonder if this might be just the kind of thing they're after.
** '''Duke Horacio:''' Would you be willing to take it to them for me?
** {{tselect|Start the Rune Mysteries quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Sure, no problem.
*** '''Duke Horacio:''' Thank you very much. You'll find the Wizards' Tower south west of here, across the bridge from Draynor Village. When you arrive, look for Sedridor. He is the Archmage of the wizards there.
*** {{tbox|pic=Air talisman detail.png|The Duke hands you the talisman.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' Not right now.
*** '''Duke Horacio:''' As you wish. Hopefully I can find someone else to help.
*** {{tact|end}}
