==Delivering the research package==
===Talking to Aubury===
* '''Aubury:''' Do you want to buy some runes?
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Yes please!}}
* {{topt|I've been sent here with a package for you.}}
** '''Player:''' I've been sent here with a package for you.
** '''Aubury:''' A package? From who?
** '''Player:''' From Sedridor at the Wizards' Tower.
** '''Aubury:''' From Sedridor? But... surely, he can't have? Please, let me have it. It must be extremely important for him to have sent a stranger.
** {{tcond|If the player has the package:}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Research package detail.png|You hand the package to Aubury.}}
*** '''Aubury:''' Now, let's have a look...
*** {{tbox|pic=Research package detail.png|Aubury goes through the package of research notes.}}
*** '''Aubury:''' This... this is incredible.
*** '''Aubury:''' My gratitude to you adventurer for bringing me these research notes. Thanks to you, I think we finally have it.
*** '''Player:''' You mean the incantation?
*** '''Aubury:''' Well when we combine my own research with this latest discovery, I think we might just...
*** '''Aubury:''' No, no, I'm getting ahead of myself. The signs are promising, but let's not jump to any conclusions just yet.
*** '''Aubury:''' Here, take these notes back to Sedridor. They should hopefully give him everything he needs.
*** {{tbox|pic=Research notes (Rune Mysteries) detail.png|Aubury hands you some research notes.}}
*** '''Aubury:''' Before you leave, why not have a cup of tea?
*** {{tselect|Select an option}}
