**** '''Player:''' {{overhead|Aaah, nothing like a nice cuppa tea!}} <!--run energy fully restored-->
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|No, thank you.}}
**** '''Player:''' No, thank you.
**** {{tact|end}}
