==Delivering the research notes==
===Talking to Sedridor===
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Ah, [player name]. How goes your quest? Have you delivered my research to Aubury yet?
* '''Player:''' Yes, I have. He gave me some notes to give to you.
* '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Wonderful! Let's have a look then.
* {{tcond|If the player has the notes:}}
** {{tbox|pic=Research notes (Rune Mysteries) detail.png|You hand the notes to Sedridor.}}
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Alright, let's see what Aubury has for us...
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Yes, this is it! The lost incantation!
** '''Player:''' So you'll be able to access that essence mine now?
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' That's right! Because of you, our order finally has a proper source of rune essence again! Thank you, friend.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' If you ever want to access the essence mine yourself, just let me know. It's the least I can do.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' I will also share the incantation with others, including Aubury. When I do, I'll let them know that you are to be given unlimited access to the mine.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Oh, and you can have this air talisman back as well. I have no further need of it, and I'm sure you will find it useful.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' In case you didn't know, the talisman can be used to craft air runes. Just take it to the Air Altar south of Falador along with some rune essence.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Don't worry if you can't find the altar. The talisman can guide you there. You may find talismans for other altars as well while adventuring. They'll let you craft other types of rune.
** '''Player:''' Great! Thanks!
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' My pleasure!
** {{Qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
** {{tselect|Select an option}}
** {{topt|Can you teleport me to the Rune Essence Mine?|quest=no}}
** {{topt|Who else knows the teleport to the Rune Essence Mine?|quest=no}}
** {{topt|Could you tell me about the old Wizards' Tower?|quest=no}}
** {{topt|I'd better get going.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'd better get going.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the notes:}}
** '''Player:''' Err, you're not going to believe this...
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' What?
** '''Player:''' I don't have them.
** '''Archmage Sedridor:''' Right... You're rather careless aren't you. I suggest you go and speak to Aubury once more. With luck he will have made copies.
** {{tact|end}}

